OL,3,CBreast cancer patients given 'more
OL,4,Cextensive than necessary' surgery,
OL,5,Csays trust
OL,7,FA North East hospital trust has
OL,8,Fapologised to breast cancer patients
OL,9,Fafter a review found some women had
OL,10,Fundergone "more extensive surgery than
OL,11,Fwas necessary".
OL,13,FThe County Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,14,FTrust issued the apology last night
OL,15,F(23 July) following a series of
OL,16,Freviews which found some breast cancer
OL,17,Fpatients received sub-standard care.
