OL,3,CBreast cancer patients given 'more
OL,4,Cextensive than necessary' surgery,
OL,5,Csays trust
OL,7,FKathryn Burn, executive director of
OL,8,Fnursing, said: "We know that some
OL,9,Fpatients have not received the
OL,10,Fstandard of care we would want for
OL,11,Fthem, or that they deserve.
OL,13,F"For some, this may have meant more
OL,14,Fextensive surgery than was necessary.
OL,15,FWe are truly sorry."
