OL,3,CBreast cancer patients given 'more
OL,4,Cextensive than necessary' surgery,
OL,5,Csays trust
OL,7,FThe trust launched a review earlier
OL,8,Fthis year following an incident of
OL,9,Fpatient safety and concerns raised
OL,10,Fthrough the Northern Cancer Alliance
OL,11,Fpeer review, which was conducted
OL,12,Fbetween April and June 2024.
OL,14,FIn 2019, a visit as part of the NHS
OL,15,FGetting It Right First Time (GRIFT)
OL,16,Fprogramme suggested the trust was an
OL,17,Foutlier in some aspects of the
OL,18,Fdelivery of breast care.
