OL,3,CBreast cancer patients given 'more
OL,4,Cextensive than necessary' surgery,
OL,5,Csays trust
OL,7,FAs a result, the Royal College of
OL,8,FSurgeons carried out an independent
OL,9,Freview of its services in January, and
OL,10,Fissued its report in April.
OL,12,FThe trust said it has identified areas
OL,13,Fwhere improvement is needed including
OL,14,Fhow surgical decisions are made, how
OL,15,Fteams work together and where outdated
OL,16,Fpractises were still in use.
OL,18,FIt also said that is has appointed two
OL,19,Fnew consultants, invested in modern
OL,20,Fequipment and strengthened their
OL,21,Fprocesses.
