OL,7,FMs Burn added: "This work is not yet
OL,8,Fcomplete, and we continue to review
OL,9,Fpatient notes.
OL,11,F'We have also set up a patient
OL,12,Fhelpline and email address where any
OL,13,Fpatients who have questions or
OL,14,Fconcerns about their care can get in
OL,15,Ftouch with us to share their
OL,16,Fexperience."
